What is MyPay?

MyPay is an online payment system. It is an online digital wallet. 

How MyPay Works

i.  Select products
ii. Create a purchase order
iii.Display payment price
iv. Confirm payment
v. Payment notice
vi. Confirm purchase
vii.Remit pament

Technology

Integrate Paypal PHP SDK into the system to allow users to pay using cards.

https://github.com/paypal/PayPal-PHP-SDK 